Package: polychoric
Type: Package
Title: Fast Polychoric Correlation for Vectors and Data Frames
Version: 0.9
Date: 2023-05-30
Author: Andrej Pawluczenko
Maintainer: Andrej Pawluczenko <a.pawluczenko@gmail.com>
Description: A wrapper for C++ routines for calculating polychoric correlation coefficients often used in social science or marketing research. Single function `polycorr()` can take in ordinal factor (possibly integer) vectors, a contingency table or a data frame and returns corresponding polychoric correlation estimates in a form of single numeric value or correlation matrix.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Suggests: tinytest
Encoding: UTF-8
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
Imports: 
    Rcpp
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppEigen
URL: https://github.com/Marwolaeth/polychoric
BugReports: https://github.com/Marwolaeth/polychoric/issues
